  "title": "FUN BRAND AMBASSADOR(FREE GYM MEMBERSHIP)",
  "description": "<p></p><h2><strong>Event Crew / Brand Engagement Representative</strong></h2><p>We’re looking for <strong>energetic and motivated Event Crew members</strong> to support customer engagement and event execution. If you enjoy meeting new people, working in a fast-paced environment, and growing your career — this role is for you.</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Promote our services with an energetic and confident approach</p></li><li><p>Engage with people from all walks of life through daily outdoor activities</p></li><li><p>Deliver excellent customer service and brand representation</p></li><li><p>Work closely with team members to ensure smooth event execution</p></li><li><p>Learn quickly and adapt in a dynamic, fast-paced environment</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Why Join Us (Perks & Benefits)</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Regional travel opportunities</strong> for events and workshops</p></li><li><p><strong>Lucrative weekly payouts</strong> with high earning potential</p></li><li><p>Ongoing <strong>training & development sessions</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong career guidance and long-term support</p></li><li><p>Clear pathway for <strong>career advancement</strong></p></li><li><p>Fun, supportive, and team-driven culture</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>No prior experience required</strong> — full training provided</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working independently and as part of a team</p></li><li><p>Basic tech skills</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude with a strong willingness to learn</p></li><li><p>Ability to communicate with <strong>Chinese-speaking customers</strong> is a plus</p></li></ul><p>🚀 <strong>Shortlisting within 2–3 working days!</strong></p><h3><strong>Job Details</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Job Types:</strong> Full-time, Internship, Fresh Graduate</p></li><li><p><strong>Salary:</strong> $2,800 – $4,000 per month</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Additional Benefits</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Additional leave</p></li><li><p>Flexible working schedule</p></li><li><p>Gym membership</p></li><li><p>Professional development programs</p></li><li><p>Opportunity for promotion to permanent employee</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Working Schedule</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Day & early shifts</p></li><li><p>Monday to Friday</p></li><li><p>Shift system</p></li><li><p>Weekend availability may be required</p></li></ul><p>📍 <strong>Work Location:</strong> In person</p>",
